      <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA02d094n4-ptr" id="PJA02d094n4">4</a>
       
   <p>Benjamin Franklin.</p>

      </div>
      <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA02d094n5-ptr" id="PJA02d094n5">5</a>
       
